---

<Layout
	title="Technical Reference | Longtex Rubber Thread"
	description="Size, diameter, area, and yield reference for Longtex natural rubber threads (density basis as published)."
	keywords="rubber thread size chart, thread yield m/kg, rubber thread diameter reference, Longtex specifications"
>
	<Header />

	<main>
		<section class="relative flex min-h-[200px] items-center justify-center bg-surface px-6 py-12 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl">Reference</h1>
		</section>

		<Section id="thread-yield" class="scroll-mt-24" title="Thread sizing & yield" alt wide>
			<p class="mb-6 text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.7] text-muted">
				Legacy technical table for extruded rubber thread: count (size), diameters, cross-sectional area, and yield. Values are
				as published for planning and conversion; confirm critical dimensions with your Longtex representative.
			</p>
			<h3 class="mx-auto mb-1 max-w-[900px] text-center text-[20px] font-bold leading-tight text-text">
				Size, Diameter, and Yield of Longtex's Threads
			</h3>
			<p class="mx-auto mb-3 max-w-[900px] text-right text-sm font-bold text-text">
				Density = 1.02(g/mm²)
			</p>
			<ReferenceSpecTable headers={threadYieldHeaders} rows={threadYieldRows} />

			<div id="conversion" class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-[900px] scroll-mt-24 border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
				<h3 class="mb-4 text-center text-[20px] font-bold leading-tight text-text">Conversion Table</h3>
				<ReferenceSpecTable rows={conversionRows} />
			</div>
		</Section>
	</main>

	<Footer
		copyright="© YEAR Longtex Rubber Industry Co., Ltd."
		address="121/32 Moo 8 Soi Suksawad 74, Suksawad Rd., Bangkru, Prapradaeng, Samutprakarn 10130 Thailand."
	/>

	<ScrollToTop />
</Layout>
